Man Up is the third album by the Danish blues-rock group The Blue Van. It was released on October 27, 2008 in Danish music stores and on iTunes under TVT Records. The song Silly Boy was featured in the Samsung Behold advertisement. The song Man Up has been featured in the TV Series 90210 and a commercial for the new season of Scrubs.
